<detall><id label=""><![CDATA[55662]]></id><title label="Titol"><![CDATA['Les Criades' at Grec]]></title><excerpt label="Resum"><![CDATA[An innovative Korean company brings one of the most famous pieces by Jean Genet to the stage at the Mercat de les Flors.]]></excerpt><content label="Contingut"><![CDATA[<p>Director Do Wan Im, founder of the Korean company Sadari Movement Laboratory, is presenting Les Criades at the Mercat de les Flors as part of the Grec 2014 summer festival in Barcelona.</p>
<p>The story of two young women who hate the woman they serve but who, at the same time, dress in her clothes, copy her and fantasise about becoming her has, in the hands of Sadari Movement Laboratory, become an imposing example of physical theatre in which a piece of furniture also plays a fundamental role.</p>
